<view class="page">

<!-- 顶部：控局航道总览 -->
<view class="hero-card">
  <view class="hero-left">
    <view class="hero-label">控局者 · 训练中枢</view>
    <view class="hero-title">从 7 天训练到完整控局体系</view>
    <view class="hero-desc">
      这里承载你的训练营进度、控局日历与后续升级路径。
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="hero-right">
    <view class="hero-stat">
      <text class="hero-stat-label">本轮训练营</text>
      <text class="hero-stat-value">{{finishedDays}} / 7 天</text>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-stat-tag">{{stageText}}</view>
  </view>
</view>

<!-- A 区：7 天风控训练营 -->
<view class="section-card">

  <view class="section-a-row section-a-row-top">
    <view class="section-a-main">
      <text class="section-tag">A. 7 天风控训练营</text>
    </view>
    <view class="section-a-btn-wrap">
      <button class="section-a-btn" bindtap="goCamp">进入训练营</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-a-row">
    <view class="section-a-main">
      <view class="section-a-title">熵盾研究院 · 控局日历</view>
      <view class="section-a-sub">统一查看训练营与多类控局排期，集中安排控局节奏</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section-a-btn-wrap">
      <button class="section-a-btn" bindtap="goToCourseList">进入控局日历</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-a-row">
    <view class="section-a-main">
      <view class="section-a-title">我的控局进度</view>
      <view class="section-a-sub">查看训练营与控局的完成情况，掌握自己的控局节奏</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section-a-btn-wrap">
      <button class="section-a-btn" bindtap="goCourseProgress">查看进度</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-meta">
    <text class="row-label">当前进度</text>
    <text class="row-value">{{finishedDays}} / 7 天</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section-goal">
    <text class="row-text section-goal-text">
      训练目标：通过 7 天，把“止损、仓位、复盘”变成你交易前后自动会做的动作。
    </text>
  </view>

  <view class="section-footer">
    <text class="section-tip">建议顺序：先完成一轮 7 天训练，再进入控局系统课与线下沙龙。</text>
  </view>
</view>

<!-- B 区：近期课程与预约（真实课表驱动） -->
<view class="section-card">
  <view class="section-header-b header-row">
    <text class="section-tag">B. 近期课与预约</text>
    <text class="header-link" bindtap="goToCourseList">查看课表</text>
  </view>
  <view class="section-sub-line">公开课 / 体验课 / 训练营 / 线下沙龙</view>

  <view class="fixed-title">控局路径 · 固定入口</view>

  <!-- loading：首次加载用骨架 -->
  <view wx:if="{{bLoading && fixedEntries.length===0}}" class="b-skeleton-wrap">
    <view class="b-skeleton-card"></view>
    <view class="b-skeleton-card"></view>
  </view>

  <view wx:elif="{{bLoading}}" class="b-hint">
    正在刷新课表...
  </view>

  <view class="b-error" wx:if="{{bErrorText}}">
    <text>{{bErrorText}}</text>
    <button class="b-retry" catchtap="onRetryFixed">重试</button>
  </view>

  <view wx:for="{{fixedEntries}}" wx:key="key" class="fixed-card {{item.isFallback?'fixed-card-fallback':''}}" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="onFixedCardTap">
    <view class="fixed-top">
      <view class="fixed-step {{item.stepClass}}">{{item.stepLabel}}</view>
      <view class="fixed-right">
        <view class="fixed-pill {{item.pillClass}}">{{item.typeLabel}}</view>
        <view class="fixed-status {{item.statusBadgeClass}}">{{item.statusText}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="fixed-name">{{item.title}}</view>
    <view class="fixed-time">{{item.timeRange}}</view>

    <view class="fixed-brief" wx:if="{{item.brief}}">
      {{item.brief}}
    </view>

    <view class="fixed-actions">
      <button class="btn-ghost {{item.isFallback?'btn-disabled':''}}" data-id="{{item.id}}" catchtap="onFixedDetailTap">查看详情</button>
      <button class="btn-primary {{item.isFallback?'btn-disabled':''}}"
        wx:if="{{item.courseType==='salon' || item.key==='salon'}}"
        data-id="{{item.id}}"
        catchtap="onFixedBookingTap">预约来访</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="b-foot">
    说明：课程时间以课表为准；线下沙龙报名后我们会联系确认来访时间。
  </view>
</view>

<!-- C 区：课程预约与渠道数据（预留） -->
<view class="section-card section-card-small">
  <view class="section-header-c">
    <text class="section-tag">C. 课程预约与渠道数据</text>
  </view>
  <view class="section-body">
    <text class="row-text">
      未来会在这里看到：每一场课程的预约人数、到课率，以及来自「小程序分享 / 老用户转介绍 / 社群渠道」等统计，用于你的市场拓展决策。
    </text>
  </view>
</view>

</view>
